<title>USA: AM International Inc Q2 Feb 1 loss narrows.</title>
<headline>AM International Inc Q2 Feb 1 loss narrows.</headline>
<dateline>MOUNT PROSPECT, Ill. 1997-03-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.12     loss	 $1.25</p>
<p> Net loss		     857     loss	 8,730</p>
<p> Revs			20,767		   40,886</p>
<p> Avg shrs		   7,008		    7,009</p>
<p>	 (All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Prior period ended January 27, 1996. Year-ago Q2 included loss of $4.4 million or $0.63/shr from discontinued operations.  </p>
<p>			6 MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.05     loss	 $1.78</p>
<p> Net loss		     338     loss	12,500</p>
<p> Revs			48,466		   83,880</p>
<p> Avg shrs		   7,008		    7,009</p>
<p>	 (All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Year-ago six month results include loss of $4.7 million, or $0.67/shr from discontinued operations.</p>
<p>In the Q1 ended November 2, 1996, AM had a $2.1 million gain primarily from divestiture of its interest in JM Japan Co Ltd.</p>
